{"doc":{"isMarkdown":false,"isTranslated":true,"isActive":false,"flaws":{},"title":"ArrayBuffer","mdn_url":"/de/docs/Web/JavaScript/Reference/Global_Objects/ArrayBuffer","locale":"de","native":"Deutsch","sidebarHTML":"<ol><li><strong><a href=\"/de/docs/Web/JavaScript/Reference/Global_Objects\">Standard-Objekte</a></strong></li><li><strong><a href=\"/de/docs/Web/JavaScript/Reference/Global_Objects/ArrayBuffer\"><code>ArrayBuffer</code></a></strong></li><li data-default-state=\"open\"><a href=\"#\"><strong>Eigenschaften</strong></a><ol><li><a href=\"/de/docs/Web/JavaScript/Reference/Global_Objects/ArrayBuffer/@@species\"><code>get ArrayBuffer[@@species]</code></a></li><li><a href=\"/de/docs/Web/JavaScript/Reference/Global_Objects/ArrayBuffer/byteLength\"><code>ArrayBuffer.prototype.byteLength</code></a></li></ol></li><li data-default-state=\"open\"><a href=\"#\"><strong>Methoden</strong></a><ol><li><a href=\"/de/docs/Web/JavaScript/Reference/Global_Objects/ArrayBuffer/isView\"><code>ArrayBuffer.isView()</code></a></li><li><a href=\"/de/docs/Web/JavaScript/Reference/Global_Objects/ArrayBuffer/slice\"><code>ArrayBuffer.prototype.slice()</code></a></li></ol></li><li><strong>Vererbung:</strong></li><li><strong><a href=\"/de/docs/Web/JavaScript/Reference/Global_Objects/Function\"><code>Function</code></a></strong></li><li><a href=\"#\"><strong>Eigenschaften</strong></a><ol><li><svg class=\"icon icon-deprecated\" tabindex=\"0\">\n    <use xlink:href=\"/assets/badges.svg#icon-deprecated\"></use>\n</svg><a href=\"/de/docs/Web/JavaScript/Reference/Global_Objects/Function/arguments\"><code>Function.prototype.arguments</code></a></li><li><svg class=\"icon icon-deprecated\" tabindex=\"0\">\n    <use xlink:href=\"/assets/badges.svg#icon-deprecated\"></use>\n</svg><a href=\"/de/docs/Web/JavaScript/Reference/Global_Objects/Function/caller\"><code>Function.prototype.caller</code></a></li><li><svg class=\"icon icon-nonstandard\" tabindex=\"0\">\n    <use xlink:href=\"/assets/badges.svg#icon-nonstandard\"></use>\n</svg><a href=\"/de/docs/Web/JavaScript/Reference/Global_Objects/Function/displayName\"><code>Function.prototype.displayName</code></a></li><li><a href=\"/de/docs/Web/JavaScript/Reference/Global_Objects/Function/length\"><code>Function.prototype.length</code></a></li><li><a href=\"/de/docs/Web/JavaScript/Reference/Global_Objects/Function/name\"><code>Function.prototype.name</code></a></li><li><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/JavaScript/Reference/Global_Objects/Function/prototype\"><code>Function.prototype.prototype</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></li></ol></li><li><a href=\"#\"><strong>Methoden</strong></a><ol><li><a href=\"/de/docs/Web/JavaScript/Reference/Global_Objects/Function/apply\"><code>Function.prototype.apply()</code></a></li><li><a href=\"/de/docs/Web/JavaScript/Reference/Global_Objects/Function/bind\"><code>Function.prototype.bind()</code></a></li><li><a href=\"/de/docs/Web/JavaScript/Reference/Global_Objects/Function/call\"><code>Function.prototype.call()</code></a></li><li><a href=\"/de/docs/Web/JavaScript/Reference/Global_Objects/Function/toString\"><code>Function.prototype.toString()</code></a></li></ol></li><li><strong><a href=\"/de/docs/Web/JavaScript/Reference/Global_Objects/Object\"><code>Object</code></a></strong></li><li><a href=\"#\"><strong>Eigenschaften</strong></a><ol><li><a href=\"/de/docs/Web/JavaScript/Reference/Global_Objects/Object/constructor\"><code>Object.prototype.constructor</code></a></li><li><svg class=\"icon icon-deprecated\" tabindex=\"0\">\n    <use xlink:href=\"/assets/badges.svg#icon-deprecated\"></use>\n</svg><a href=\"/de/docs/Web/JavaScript/Reference/Global_Objects/Object/proto\"><code>Object.prototype.__proto__</code></a></li></ol></li><li><a href=\"#\"><strong>Methoden</strong></a><ol><li><svg class=\"icon icon-deprecated\" tabindex=\"0\">\n    <use xlink:href=\"/assets/badges.svg#icon-deprecated\"></use>\n</svg><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/JavaScript/Reference/Global_Objects/Object/__defineGetter__\"><code>Object.prototype.__defineGetter__()</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></li><li><svg class=\"icon icon-deprecated\" tabindex=\"0\">\n    <use xlink:href=\"/assets/badges.svg#icon-deprecated\"></use>\n</svg><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/JavaScript/Reference/Global_Objects/Object/__defineSetter__\"><code>Object.prototype.__defineSetter__()</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></li><li><svg class=\"icon icon-deprecated\" tabindex=\"0\">\n    <use xlink:href=\"/assets/badges.svg#icon-deprecated\"></use>\n</svg><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/JavaScript/Reference/Global_Objects/Object/__lookupGetter__\"><code>Object.prototype.__lookupGetter__()</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></li><li><svg class=\"icon icon-deprecated\" tabindex=\"0\">\n    <use xlink:href=\"/assets/badges.svg#icon-deprecated\"></use>\n</svg><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/JavaScript/Reference/Global_Objects/Object/__lookupSetter__\"><code>Object.prototype.__lookupSetter__()</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></li><li><a href=\"/de/docs/Web/JavaScript/Reference/Global_Objects/Object/hasOwnProperty\"><code>Object.prototype.hasOwnProperty()</code></a></li><li><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/JavaScript/Reference/Global_Objects/Object/isPrototypeOf\"><code>Object.prototype.isPrototypeOf()</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></li><li><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/JavaScript/Reference/Global_Objects/Object/propertyIsEnumerable\"><code>Object.prototype.propertyIsEnumerable()</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></li><li><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/JavaScript/Reference/Global_Objects/Object/setPrototypeOf\"><code>Object.setPrototypeOf()</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></li><li><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/JavaScript/Reference/Global_Objects/Object/toLocaleString\"><code>Object.prototype.toLocaleString()</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></li><li><a href=\"/de/docs/Web/JavaScript/Reference/Global_Objects/Object/toString\"><code>Object.prototype.toString()</code></a></li><li><a href=\"/de/docs/Web/JavaScript/Reference/Global_Objects/Object/valueOf\"><code>Object.prototype.valueOf()</code></a></li></ol></li></ol>","body":[{"type":"prose","value":{"id":null,"title":null,"isH3":false,"content":"<div id=\"sect1\"></div>\n\n<p>Das&nbsp;<code><strong>ArrayBuffer</strong></code> Objekt repräsentiert einen generischen Buffer mit fester Länge. Der Inhalt eines <code>ArrayBuffer</code>s&nbsp;kann nicht direkt bearbeitet&nbsp;werden; stattdessen wird eines der&nbsp;<a href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/JavaScript/Reference/Global_Objects/TypedArray\" class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\">typisierten Array-Objekte (en-US)</a>&nbsp;oder ein <a href=\"/de/docs/Web/JavaScript/Reference/Global_Objects/DataView\"><code>DataView</code></a> Objekt verwendet, welches den Buffer in einem bestimmten Format repräsentiert und von welchem aus sein Inhalt bearbeitet werden kann.</p>\n\n<div id=\"sect2\"><iframe class=\"interactive\" height=\"490\" src=\"https://interactive-examples.mdn.mozilla.net/pages/js/arraybuffer-constructor.html\" title=\"MDN Web Docs Interactive Example\" loading=\"lazy\"></iframe></div>"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"syntax","title":"Syntax","isH3":false,"content":"<pre class=\"syntaxbox notranslate\">new ArrayBuffer(length)\n</pre>"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"parameter","title":"Parameter","isH3":true,"content":"<dl>\n <dt id=\"length\">length</dt>\n <dd>Die Größe, in Bytes, des zu erstellenden <code>ArrayBuffer</code>.</dd>\n</dl>"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"rückgabewert","title":"Rückgabewert","isH3":true,"content":"<p>Ein neues&nbsp;<code>ArrayBuffer </code>Objekt der angegebenen Länge. Der Inhalt wird auf 0 initialisiert.</p>"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"ausnahmen","title":"Ausnahmen","isH3":true,"content":"<p>Ein <a class=\"page-not-created\" title=\"Die Beschreibung hierüber wurde bisher noch nicht geschrieben. Bitte überlege, mitzuwirken!\"><code>RangeError</code></a> wird erhoben wenn die Länge größer als <a href=\"/de/docs/Web/JavaScript/Reference/Global_Objects/Number/MAX_SAFE_INTEGER\"><code>Number.MAX_SAFE_INTEGER</code></a> (&gt;= 2 ** 53) oder negativ ist.</p>"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"beschreibung","title":"Beschreibung","isH3":false,"content":"<p>Der&nbsp;<code>ArrayBuffer</code> Konstruktor erstellt einen neuen&nbsp;<code>ArrayBuffer </code>der angegebenen Länge in Bytes.</p>"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"einen_arraybuffer_von_existierenden_daten_erstellen","title":"Einen ArrayBuffer von existierenden Daten erstellen","isH3":true,"content":"<ul>\n <li><a href=\"/en-US/docs/Glossary/Base64#appendix.3a_decode_a_base64_string_to_uint8array_or_arraybuffer\" class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\">Von einem&nbsp;Base64-String (en-US)</a></li>\n <li><a href=\"/de/docs/Web/API/FileReader#readasarraybuffer()\">Von einer lokalen Datei</a></li>\n</ul>"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"eigenschaften","title":"Eigenschaften","isH3":false,"content":"<dl>\n <dt id=\"arraybuffer.length\"><code>ArrayBuffer.length</code></dt>\n <dd>Der Wert des&nbsp;<code>ArrayBuffer</code> Konstruktors für die Länge.</dd>\n <dt id=\"get_arraybufferspecies\"><a href=\"/de/docs/Web/JavaScript/Reference/Global_Objects/ArrayBuffer/@@species\"><code>get ArrayBuffer[@@species]</code></a></dt>\n <dd>Die Konstruktor-Funktion um abgeleitete Objekte zu erstellen.</dd>\n <dt id=\"arraybuffer.prototype_en-us\"><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/JavaScript/Reference/Global_Objects/ArrayBuffer\"><code>ArrayBuffer.prototype</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></dt>\n <dd>Erlaubt das Hinzufügen von Eigenschaften zu allen <code>ArrayBuffer </code>Objekten.</dd>\n</dl>"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"methoden","title":"Methoden","isH3":false,"content":"<dl>\n <dt id=\"arraybuffer.isviewarg\"><a href=\"/de/docs/Web/JavaScript/Reference/Global_Objects/ArrayBuffer/isView\"><code>ArrayBuffer.isView(arg)</code></a></dt>\n <dd>Gibt&nbsp;<code>true</code>&nbsp;zurück wenn&nbsp;<code>arg</code>&nbsp;eines der Views des&nbsp;<code>ArrayBuffers </code>ist, wie zum Beispiel&nbsp;die&nbsp;<a href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/JavaScript/Reference/Global_Objects/TypedArray\" class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\">typisierten&nbsp;Array-Objekt (en-US)</a>e&nbsp;oder ein <a href=\"/de/docs/Web/JavaScript/Reference/Global_Objects/DataView\"><code>DataView</code></a>. Ansonsten wird&nbsp;<code>false</code>&nbsp;zurückgegeben.</dd>\n <dt id=\"arraybuffer.transferoldbuffer_newbytelength\"><a class=\"page-not-created\" title=\"Die Beschreibung hierüber wurde bisher noch nicht geschrieben. Bitte überlege, mitzuwirken!\"><code>ArrayBuffer.transfer(oldBuffer [, newByteLength])</code></a> <svg class=\"icon icon-experimental\" tabindex=\"0\">\n    <use xlink:href=\"/assets/badges.svg#icon-experimental\"></use>\n</svg></dt>\n <dd>\n <div class=\"line\" id=\"file-arraybuffer-transfer-lc6\">Gibt einen neuen&nbsp;<code>ArrayBuffer</code> zurück, dessen Inhalt von den Daten des&nbsp;<code>oldBuffer</code>s genommen wird und dann entweder abgeschnitten oder mit Null auf <code>newByteLength</code>&nbsp;erweitert wird.</div>\n </dd>\n</dl>"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"instanzen","title":"Instanzen","isH3":false,"content":"<p>Alle&nbsp;<code>ArrayBuffer</code> Instanzen erben von&nbsp;<a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/JavaScript/Reference/Global_Objects/ArrayBuffer\"><code>ArrayBuffer.prototype</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a>.</p>"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"eigenschaften_2","title":"Eigenschaften","isH3":true,"content":"<p>{{page('de/Web/JavaScript/Reference/Global_Objects/ArrayBuffer/prototype','Eigenschaften')}}</p>"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"methoden_2","title":"Methoden","isH3":true,"content":"<p>{{page('de/Web/JavaScript/Reference/Global_Objects/ArrayBuffer/prototype','Methoden')}}</p>\n\n<dl>\n <dt id=\"arraybuffer.slice\"><a href=\"/de/docs/Web/JavaScript/Reference/Global_Objects/ArrayBuffer/slice\"><code>ArrayBuffer.slice()</code></a> <svg class=\"icon icon-nonstandard\" tabindex=\"0\">\n    <use xlink:href=\"/assets/badges.svg#icon-nonstandard\"></use>\n</svg></dt>\n <dd>Hat die selbe Funktion wie <a href=\"/de/docs/Web/JavaScript/Reference/Global_Objects/ArrayBuffer/slice\"><code>ArrayBuffer.prototype.slice()</code></a>.</dd>\n</dl>"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"beispiel","title":"Beispiel","isH3":false,"content":"<p>In diesem Beispiel erstellen wir einen 8-byte Puffer mit einem <a href=\"/de/docs/Web/JavaScript/Reference/Global_Objects/Int32Array\"><code>Int32Array</code></a> View, um auf den Puffer zu verweisen:</p>\n\n<div class=\"code-example\"><pre class=\"brush: js notranslate\"><code><span class=\"token keyword\">var</span> buffer <span class=\"token operator\">=</span> <span class=\"token keyword\">new</span> <span class=\"token class-name\">ArrayBuffer</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token number\">8</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n<span class=\"token keyword\">var</span> view   <span class=\"token operator\">=</span> <span class=\"token keyword\">new</span> <span class=\"token class-name\">Int32Array</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span>buffer<span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span></code></pre></div>"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"spezifikationen","title":"Spezifikationen","isH3":false,"content":"<table class=\"standard-table\">\n <tbody>\n  <tr>\n   <th scope=\"col\">Spezifikation</th>\n   <th scope=\"col\">Status</th>\n   <th scope=\"col\">Kommentar</th>\n  </tr>\n  <tr>\n   <td><a href=\"https://www.khronos.org/registry/typedarray/specs/latest/\" hreflang=\"en\" lang=\"en\" class=\"external\" title=\"Die 'Typed Array Specification' Spezifikation\" rel=\" noopener\">Typed Array Specification</a></td>\n   <td><span class=\"spec-obsolete\">Veraltet</span></td>\n   <td>Ersetzt durch ECMAScript 6.</td>\n  </tr>\n  <tr>\n   <td><a href=\"https://www.ecma-international.org/ecma-262/6.0/#sec-arraybuffer-constructor\" hreflang=\"en\" lang=\"en\" class=\"external\" rel=\" noopener\">ECMAScript 2015 (6th Edition, ECMA-262)<br><small lang=\"de\">Die Definition von 'ArrayBuffer' in dieser Spezifikation.</small></a></td>\n   <td><span class=\"spec-standard\">Standard</span></td>\n   <td>Initiale Definition im ECMA Standard. Spezifiziert, dass&nbsp;<code>new</code> benötigt wird.</td>\n  </tr>\n  <tr>\n   <td><a href=\"https://tc39.es/ecma262/#sec-arraybuffer-constructor\" hreflang=\"en\" lang=\"en\" class=\"external\" rel=\" noopener\">ECMAScript (ECMA-262)<br><small lang=\"de\">Die Definition von 'ArrayBuffer' in dieser Spezifikation.</small></a></td>\n   <td><span class=\"spec-living\">Lebender Standard</span></td>\n   <td>&nbsp;</td>\n  </tr>\n </tbody>\n</table>"}},{"type":"browser_compatibility","value":{"title":"Browserkompatibilität","id":"browserkompatibilität","isH3":false,"query":"javascript.builtins.ArrayBuffer","dataURL":"/de/docs/Web/JavaScript/Reference/Global_Objects/ArrayBuffer/bcd.json"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":null,"title":null,"isH3":false,"content":"<p></p><p></p>"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"kompatibilitätshinweis","title":"Kompatibilitätshinweis","isH3":false,"content":"<p>Seit ECMAScript 2015 müssen&nbsp;<code>ArrayBuffer</code> Konstruktor mit einem <a href=\"/de/docs/Web/JavaScript/Reference/Operators/new\"><code>new</code></a> Operator konstruiert werden. Einen&nbsp;<code>ArrayBuffer</code> Konstruktor als Funktion aufzurufen ohne&nbsp;<code>new</code>&nbsp;ab sofort einen&nbsp;<a href=\"/de/docs/Web/JavaScript/Reference/Global_Objects/TypeError\"><code>TypeError</code></a> erheben.</p>\n\n<div class=\"code-example\"><pre class=\"brush: js example-bad notranslate\"><code><span class=\"token keyword\">var</span> dv <span class=\"token operator\">=</span> <span class=\"token function\">ArrayBuffer</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token number\">10</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n<span class=\"token comment\">// TypeError: Einen eingebauten ArrayBuffer-Konstruktor</span>\n<span class=\"token comment\">// ohne new aufzurufen ist nicht erlaubt.</span></code></pre></div>\n\n<div class=\"code-example\"><pre class=\"brush: js example-good notranslate\"><code><span class=\"token keyword\">var</span> dv <span class=\"token operator\">=</span> <span class=\"token keyword\">new</span> <span class=\"token class-name\">ArrayBuffer</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token number\">10</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span></code></pre></div>"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"siehe_auch","title":"Siehe auch","isH3":false,"content":"<ul>\n <li><a href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/JavaScript/Typed_arrays\">JavaScript typed arrays</a></li>\n <li><a class=\"page-not-created\" title=\"Die Beschreibung hierüber wurde bisher noch nicht geschrieben. Bitte überlege, mitzuwirken!\"><code>SharedArrayBuffer</code></a></li>\n</ul>"}}],"toc":[{"text":"Syntax","id":"syntax"},{"text":"Beschreibung","id":"beschreibung"},{"text":"Eigenschaften","id":"eigenschaften"},{"text":"Methoden","id":"methoden"},{"text":"Instanzen","id":"instanzen"},{"text":"Beispiel","id":"beispiel"},{"text":"Spezifikationen","id":"spezifikationen"},{"text":"Browserkompatibilität","id":"browserkompatibilität"},{"text":"Kompatibilitätshinweis","id":"kompatibilitätshinweis"},{"text":"Siehe auch","id":"siehe_auch"}],"summary":"Das ArrayBuffer Objekt repräsentiert einen generischen Buffer mit fester Länge. Der Inhalt eines ArrayBuffers kann nicht direkt bearbeitet werden; stattdessen wird eines der typisierten Array-Objekte (en-US) oder ein DataView Objekt verwendet, welches den Buffer in einem bestimmten Format repräsentiert und von welchem aus sein Inhalt bearbeitet werden kann.","popularity":0.0004,"modified":"2022-07-19T02:29:32.000Z","other_translations":[{"title":"ArrayBuffer","locale":"en-US","native":"English (US)"},{"title":"ArrayBuffer","locale":"es","native":"Español"},{"title":"ArrayBuffer","locale":"fr","native":"Français"},{"title":"ArrayBuffer","locale":"ja","native":"日本語"},{"title":"ArrayBuffer","locale":"ko","native":"한국어"},{"title":"ArrayBuffer","locale":"pl","native":"Polski"},{"title":"ArrayBuffer","locale":"pt-BR","native":"Português (do Brasil)"},{"title":"ArrayBuffer","locale":"ru","native":"Русский"},{"title":"ArrayBuffer","locale":"zh-CN","native":"中文 (简体)"},{"title":"ArrayBuffer","locale":"zh-TW","native":"正體中文 (繁體)"}],"source":{"folder":"de/web/javascript/reference/global_objects/arraybuffer","github_url":"https://github.com/mdn/translated-content/blob/main/files/de/web/javascript/reference/global_objects/arraybuffer/index.html","last_commit_url":"https://github.com/mdn/translated-content/commit/5fe4ab11259b37914fab41914e84897fea47d143","filename":"index.html"},"parents":[{"uri":"/de/docs/Web","title":"Webtechnologien für Entwickler"},{"uri":"/de/docs/Web/JavaScript","title":"JavaScript"},{"uri":"/de/docs/Web/JavaScript/Reference","title":"JavaScript-Referenz"},{"uri":"/de/docs/Web/JavaScript/Reference/Global_Objects","title":"Globale Objekte"},{"uri":"/de/docs/Web/JavaScript/Reference/Global_Objects/ArrayBuffer","title":"ArrayBuffer"}],"pageTitle":"ArrayBuffer - JavaScript | MDN","noIndexing":false}}